{
  "texts": [
    "To display the Top-N% of highlights, we retain the highest N% of highlight scores and set the remainder to zero.",
    "Each word's highlight intensity is determined by the average non-zero highlight scores of its tokens.",
    "To prevent overwhelming the participants while maintaining NDA integrity, we give them the option to expand/collapse sections with no highlights.",
    "An example is shown in Fig. 13.",
    "Influential training examples."
  ]
}